DFS + BT to find all and return candidate `paths` of cardinality `K` and total `T`.

---

**Similiar Problems:**

* [39. Combination Sum](https://leetcode.com/problems/combination-sum/discuss/506331/a-few-solutions)
* [40. Combination Sum II](https://leetcode.com/problems/combination-sum-ii/discuss/506360/a-few-solutions)

---

*Kotlin*
```
class Solution {
    fun combinationSum3(K: Int, T: Int): List<List<Int>> {
        var paths = mutableListOf<List<Int>>()
        fun go(start: Int = 1, t: Int = 0, path: MutableList<Int> = mutableListOf<Int>()) {
            if (path.size == K) {
                if (t == T)
                    paths.add(path.toList())
                return
            }
            for (x in start..9) {
                path.add(x)
                go(x + 1, t + x, path)
                path.removeAt(path.lastIndex)
            }
        }
        go()
        return paths
    }
}
```

